@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About</PageTitle>

<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col text-center mt-4">
            <h2 class="fs-1 text-uppercase text-dark mb-3">About Us</h2>
            <h4 class="fw-bold">Our Journey Through Time</h4>
            <img src="images/banner.png" class="img-fluid d-block my-4" alt="Our Story">
            <h6 class="text-muted">Discover the stories behind each timeless piece. Our dedication to preserving history is only matched by our commitment to our customers.</h6>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container my-5">
    <div class="timeline">
        <div class="line"></div>

        <!-- Inception of Mr C's Vintage Vehicles -->
        <div class="row m-0">
            <div class="col-sm-6">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col">
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h5 class="card-title">The Beginning</h5>
                                <p class="card-text">In 1982, Mr. C launched a car rental company with an extraordinary fleet of well-preserved older vehicles, which by the 1990s, evolved into a sought-after vintage car rental service, tapping into the era's growing nostalgia for classic autos. His passion for maintaining classic cars transformed an ordinary rental service into a sanctuary for vintage car enthusiasts.</p>
                                <p class="card-text"><small class="text-muted">Started in 1982</small></p>
                            </div>
                            <img src="images/about/0.png" class="card-img-bottom" alt="The Vintage Beginning">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- First Fleet Expansion -->
        <div class="row m-0">
            <div class="col-sm-6 offset-sm-6">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col">
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h5 class="card-title">Expanding Horizons</h5>
                                <p class="card-text">By 1990, Mr C's fleet grew to include over 20 meticulously restored vintage cars, marking a new chapter of growth and passion for the past.</p>
                                <p class="card-text"><small class="text-muted">Expansion in 1990</small></p>
                            </div>
                            <img src="images/about/1.png" class="card-img-bottom" alt="Expanding Horizons">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Milestone Event -->
        <div class="row m-0">
            <div class="col-sm-6">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col">
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h5 class="card-title">Milestone Celebration</h5>
                                <p class="card-text">In 2000, Mr C's celebrated its 1000th rental, a testament to the timeless allure of its classic vehicles and exceptional service.</p>
                                <p class="card-text"><small class="text-muted">1000th Rental in 2000</small></p>
                            </div>
                            <img src="images/about/2.png" class="card-img-bottom" alt="Milestone Celebration">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Renovation and Innovation -->
        <div class="row m-0">
            <div class="col-sm-6 offset-sm-6">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col">
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h5 class="card-title">Renaissance of the Classics</h5>
                                <p class="card-text">2010 marked a renaissance for Mr C's, with a state-of-the-art showroom and garage that blends the classic with the contemporary.</p>
                                <p class="card-text"><small class="text-muted">Showroom Renovation in 2010</small></p>
                            </div>
                            <img src="images/about/3.png" class="card-img-bottom" alt="Renaissance of the Classics">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Current Success -->
        <div class="row m-0">
            <div class="col-sm-6">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col">
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h5 class="card-title">Continuing the Legacy</h5>
                                <p class="card-text">Today, Mr C's Vintage Vehicle Rental thrives, offering an ever-expanding collection of over 200 classic cars to aficionados and newcomers alike.</p>
                                <p class="card-text"><small class="text-muted">Current Day Success</small></p>
                            </div>
                            <img src="images/about/4.png" class="card-img-bottom" alt="Continuing the Legacy">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>
